---
import Layout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../../components/Section.astro";
import ExperienceBadge from "../../components/ExperienceBadge.astro";

import softwareExperience from "../../data/softwareExperience";
---

<Layout
  title="Software"
  description="Matthew Ubalde software development portfolio. Have experience in C/C++, C#, and Java to create computer softwares."
  enableNav
>
  <Fragment slot="sidebar">
    <h1>Software Development</h1>
    <p class="font-light">
      Have experience in C++, C# and Java to create computer applications.
    </p>
    <p class="font-light">
      Learned numerous programming languages from web, game, and to software
      development. Able to adapt and learn quickly when needed.
    </p>
  </Fragment>
  <Section>
    <h1 class="text-center mb-8">Software Experiences</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-stretch gap-4">
      {softwareExperience.map((s) => <ExperienceBadge src={s} />)}
    </div>
  </Section>
  <Section class="flex flex-col justify-center gap-8 text-center">
    <h1>Experiences in Fanshawe</h1>
    <p>Throughout my CPA3 program, I've learned many things.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Create tools and extend the 3D renderer made in OpenGL and C++ despite
        the time and pressure for 2 months with a 4 month semester worth of
        content.
      </li>
      <li>
        Able to use problem-solving skills and logically debug application.
      </li>
      <li>
        Able to create a mobile task-management application with easy-controls,
        authentication, and potiential cloud support.
      </li>
      <li>
        Able to create efficient databases by normalizing the objects we're
        storing, and use indexes to optimize it further.
      </li>
      <li>Able to create queries in database for any needs.</li>
    </ul>
  </Section>
</Layout>
